Module atu.software
Package ie.atu.sw.model

Class ModuleServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
ie.atu.sw.model.ModuleServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
ModuleService, Serializable
public class ModuleServiceImpl extends Object implements ModuleService, Serializable
Implementation of the ModuleService interface. This class provides functionality to manage modules, including creating, updating, and listing module information. It interacts with users through the command line to gather input and display information.
